node.text:
Proud to launch a new programme with @manchesterunitedfoundation through the @waynerooneyfoundation. 🙌

Rooney’s Inclusive Reds launched at @manchesterunited’s training ground yesterday and aims to promote inclusion for all in lots of different activities. Looking forward to meeting everyone soon 🙂❤️
